description: Well, I'm 5'9", heavy build, brown eyes...oh, you mean the level! I have a terrible tendency to start building a level and then leave bits of it sitting around for ages. I discovered part of this level still waiting to be completed, and I had a sudden burst of inspiration, so here it is. The level is quite tricky - ammo is limited and there is much switch-pressing, hence the name. Let me know what you think!
